Old Madam's illness is indeed peculiar.

44
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,400
She had severe stomachache in the afternoon.

45
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,000
Vomit and diarrhea.

46
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,320
Her body is in a continuous twitch.

47
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:49,400
