124
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,640
It's not for sure. Not for sure.

125
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:19,920
Miss.

126
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,680
Please watch your own health.

127
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,920
