128
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,760
Don't be too startled, Madam.

129
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,920
I will do my utmost.

130
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:33,400
For safety measure,

131
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,840
I will go seeing what Old Madam's leftover

132
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,960
