133
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,680
I'll have someone go with you. Okay.

134
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,240
My courtesy to you.

135
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,000
Alright.

136
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:57,960
Xiaotao.

